title: Introducing: De La Torre
body:
Getting some serious Tove Lo vibes from Nashville’s **De La Torre** on her debut single, _Push Me Pull Me_.

Never underestimate the power of an absolutely killer chorus. Check out Push Me Pull Me below.

Like this? Follow our [On Repeat Playlist](https://open.spotify.com/user/crackintheroad/playlist/1UB6gJIZpmiO0H2zmSbg02) for a handpicked selection of the very best in new music; updated weekly.
